      <h1>DevOps: Why the Startup CEO Should Care (and you should too)</h1>
      <ul>
        <li><em>Tech</em></li>
        <li><%= t('speaker-details.length') %>: 45 Min</li>
        <li><%= t('speaker-details.language') %>: EN</li>
